parsed.fixed_xml: <ITEM><TEXT>7. Denen Herren Negotianten, welche das bekannte Wechsel-Buch: <BIBL><TITLE>La Banque rendue facile aux principales Nations de l'Europe</TITLE></BIBL> haben, zu wissen gethan, dass der Author desselben, <PERSON>Giraudeau</PERSON>, solches mit einem dritten Supplement vermehren, auch das ganze Werk durch Subscriptionen zum zweiten Mal drucken lassen wird, wovon das Project bei Herrn <PERSON>Samuel Haag</PERSON> dem <PROFESSION>Buchbinder</PROFESSION> im <LOCATION>gelben Horn am Spahlenberg</LOCATION> zu haben, auch bei ihm zu subscribiren ist.</TEXT></ITEM>
parsed.explanation: Corrected typos and a character encoding error in the French book title and the main German text. The author's name 'Gixauidenae' was identified as a probable transcription error for 'Giraudeau', the known author of the work, and the surrounding tag was corrected from <BIBL> to a more appropriate <PERSON> tag. Additional semantic tags were added for the bookbinder (<PERSON>, <PROFESSION>) and the location (<LOCATION>). Archaic German spellings were modernized for improved readability (e.g., 'gantze Werck' to 'ganze Werk', 'bey' to 'bei').
